{"tid":1444974,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"兩隻速龍落單捉義士，百幾日當場快速跑走，只得一人掉頭救人","createTime":"2019-08-11T13:39:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T13:46:41.000Z","uid":141879,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7bdd4c77c7fc027a582bca97df31da9a755f9359","tid":1444974,"uid":141879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:39:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://sendvid.com/yng1qyi1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fyng1qyi1&d=4z%2BvbskHrV%2FWTILUlLswqkzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=166830cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sendvid.com/yng1qyi1</a><br />\n<br />\n大佬呀，真係洗唔洗咁驚呀，我地有百幾人，人地先得兩隻速龍，百幾人經過都唔救人。<br />\n<br />\n如果再係咁既心態，我相信10隻速龍沖過黎，百幾人既防線唔洗5秒就崩潰。"},{"pid":"f147da0978fb43942dfa7b053a525cd254fec768","tid":1444974,"uid":141879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:42:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd44b6e5adb85be1c2e4c732660a84f7eb972097","tid":1444974,"uid":141879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:46:41.000Z","msg":"不如諗下戰略上可以點改進，大家都沖唔開心理關卡"}]}